Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才真是嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是世事難料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,六花·朝日 我要將你收入麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不小心拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是出乎意料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 最後那麼有戲劇性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在都還激動著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼她突然要拉六花入伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:00:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她們認識的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,CHU²倒是來過我們的主辦演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒和LOCK說過話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是看了Galaxy的官網之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那個官網全是在介紹我們這些樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,根本就沒寫LOCK的訊息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因為LOCK是個很強的吉他手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 就是說這件事她們是從哪知道的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是偶然發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 她們自己能發現也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沙綾？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然她們的態度是有點強硬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是對樂隊的熱情那麼強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得她們是真心喜歡著音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 她還聽過我和瑞衣都不知道的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mortin的秘密演唱會的原聲帶她也有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,CHU²不光是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,還追求著震撼人心的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定是在某個地方被LOCK的吉他感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是LOCK已經拒絕了她的邀請了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我的話… 那種情況下可能不敢拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是LOCK啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs39\pos(1023,977)}鎖住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 要是答應了肯定也會害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 香澄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,BanG Dream! 女子樂隊挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,當然要參加啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她說過要毀掉我們 沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,躲進桌子底下的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,多惠 我撓我撓…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 竟然不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對我不管用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,還是不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,總感覺這比賽陣容越來越豪華了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,友希那學姐她們怎麼決定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不參加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那針對Future World Fes的日程表就這麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明明參加的話肯定能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這樣練習的時間就要延長了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 要是再加下去 就要沒時間玩遊戲了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天真是太混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,讓開 讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:54.43,upper,,0,0,0,,你們別擠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 這不是RAS的CHU²嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你們給我讓一讓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是Celosia女子學院的校服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,還是一所成績優秀的知名國際學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是RAISE A SUILEN的製作人CHU²
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你找我們六花有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,經理人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就省事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,容我再說一遍 我是來招募六花·朝日的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,經理人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,明日香 對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,六花？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦… 沒有預約就進去可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,您好 我叫CHU²
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想申請參觀學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:06:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我對羽丘女校的教育理念深感贊同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說朝日被挖牆腳了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,太厲害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還是RAS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟她吉他那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這話都傳開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼她要來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明都拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你拒絕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她那麼強硬 我有點害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,壓扁壓扁 揉一揉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,揉一揉呀揉一揉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,揉一揉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要是真的同意 PoPiPa就要被揉成糰子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我決不讓她們揉掉PoPiPa！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,揉糰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,高一年級A班的朝日六花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,請馬上前往學生會辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高一A班的朝日六花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,請問 是您在找我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真是沒禮貌 把人說得像鬼怪一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,無關人員不能擅自進來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿到了參觀學校的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 她是客人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這是您的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,您不上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我都拿完學分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下要報到的日子也就這麼點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不說那種事了 你趕緊加入我的樂隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,請問 你們是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的吉他手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,才不好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是加入我這支最強樂隊的好機會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,最強？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes！我要用我的音樂摧毀這個女子樂團時代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好怕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin a new world 開創新世界哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,時間到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,下午的課馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你好好上課哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我來接你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,PAREO我也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,上 PAREO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,明日香 你不是體育社團的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是游泳的啦 根本跑不動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個 違反校規了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不推搡 不奔跑 不跟陌生人走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那位不是RAS的製作人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到BanG Dream的決賽竟然和大地藏慶典的日子衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:21.20,Tips,,0,0,0,,註：地藏慶典是本作取景地江戶川橋地區商店街舉辦的慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不參加真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是商店街最大的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不上場誰上場對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們用我們自己的方法登上武道館就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有商店街之處便有摩卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,六花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是LOCK嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她們在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我說經理人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,六花跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不是經理人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,CHU²大人 在那邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊是哪邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且為什麼我要做這種事… 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在那邊 右邊右邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,六花快跑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你們少嚷嚷！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,CHU²大人 你後面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她那麼小 還那麼迷糊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要逃掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 距離日落還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,還有人在靜靜等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要好好報答他的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,奔跑吧 梅洛斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.07,Tips,,0,0,0,,註：出自太宰治同名小說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有看見個眼鏡女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,眼鏡女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,指的是朝日六花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,六花她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 她說讓我保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,PAREO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不在 給她逃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要不改天再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不 明明我終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,文化祭上六花·朝日的演奏你也看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她的第一個音就讓我覺得RAS需要的就是這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,六花的吉他水平可不是開玩笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,CHU²大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要不去那邊找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不小心拿了這麼多可樂餅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她們不會跟到這來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,六花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,CHU²她現在在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,六花你對樂隊不感興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,PAREO 你在哪裡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然連個飲料都買不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你要皇家奶茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,湊友希那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘記帶錢包了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不帶現金主義的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,黑咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然讓敵人送我咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我想聽你的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過了 你會接受挑戰的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,RAS要成為能毀掉Roselia的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還要順便毀一下Poppin'Party
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我之所以拒絕你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為Roselia不是用來展示你的音樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的音樂有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想要創造音樂和成員都完美的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不需要妥協的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,友希那 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你請我的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也就這會兒能囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.20,upper,,0,0,0,,喂 給我停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:25.88,upper,,0,0,0,,停下 別跑馬路上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,又是她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,友希那你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,明天下午5點起我們要與對手樂隊會面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,從明天過後 練習時間延長2小時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,週末的練習室也儘量確保了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,請各位注意確認自己的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但確實感受到Future World Fes到來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,亞子會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,說到這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想參加BanG Dream! 女子樂隊挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 友希那 Future World Fes呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,當然也要參加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,亞子我倒是挺高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就剩幾個月了 應該專心在Future World Fes上才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼忙的日程也是為了它才安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們很像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,PAREO 拿肉乾來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你心情挺差嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然讓她逃走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為你老追她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要是不追哪能抓得住她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,隨你便了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,您要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她們不至於跑到這裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,突然叫你 不好意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,打掃完以後你就可以用這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也是一團糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真累
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到她們竟然追到學校來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,六花你對樂隊不感興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,倒不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,CHU²她比任何人都要渴望著你的才華
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我們永遠歡迎您的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,請隨時光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,益木 你來練習了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要把我揉成糰子嗎 是這樣吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢 方言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷 好冷！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,請問 要去哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好高級的大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小心摔倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,益木？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,您不是回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這是CHU²大人的私人工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有事啊 事太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她這不是嚇著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你是回心轉意了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,到底如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,音樂可不會撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,來合奏一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才一直在這麼叫 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,益木她好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,讓她盡情發揮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我站你旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要彈什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就R·I·O·T吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她聽過一遍的曲子就已經耳扒下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那你沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯嘛 挺好配合的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 您彈得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要察言觀色的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry 不合格
